body: Hehehehe I’m waiting for those fake ass fans to show their true colours if and when the boys reveal that they’re dating!!😂 Like… THEY’RE HUMANS!!! Kpop idols are humans!! They’re allowed to date!! They’re allowed to get married!! They’re allowed to be happy because they’re HUMANS!! They’re not dolls!! They have lives!!! And no one has a say in what they should or should not do!! If you truly “love” them, then respect and support them, because that’s what fans do!!!
